          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-1" n="1">1<lb/>In Beauty or Witt</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-2" n="2">No Mortall as Yett</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-3" n="3">To question the Empire has dar'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-4" n="4">But men of discerning</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-5" n="5">Have thought y<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> in Learning,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-6" n="6">To Yeild to a Lady was hard.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-7" n="7"><lb/>2_Impertinent Schools,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-8" n="8">With musty dull Rules,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-9" n="9">Have Reading to Ladies deny'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-10" n="10">So Papists refuse</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-11" n="11">The Bible to use,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-12" n="12">Least Flocks shoul'd be wise as their Guide.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-13" n="13"><lb/>3_'Twas a woman at first,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-14" n="14">(Indeed she was curs'd)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-15" n="15">In Knowledge y<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> tasted delight;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-16" n="16">And Sages agree,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-17" n="17">The Law shou'd decree</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-18" n="18">To the first of Possessors y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Right</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-19" n="19"><lb/>4_Then bravely Fair Dame</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-20" n="20">Renew the old Claim,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-21" n="21">That to y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> whole sex does belong;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-22" n="22">And let Men receive</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-23" n="23">From a second bright Eve,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-24" n="24">The Knowledge of Right &amp; of Wrong.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-25" n="25"><lb/>5_But as the first Eve</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-26" n="26">Hard Doom did receive,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-27" n="27">When only one Apple had she,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-28" n="28">What a punishment now</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-29" n="29">Must be found out for You,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z730050O-line-30" n="30">Who have tasted, &amp; robb'd, y<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> whole Tree.</l>
          </lg>
